<section class="section">
  <div class="section__inner" style="max-width:720px;">
    <h1 class="section__heading">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <p class="section__subtitle">Quick answers to common questions.</p>

    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-item__question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('faq-item--open')">What materials do you use?</div>
        <div class="faq-item__answer"><p>We prioritize natural, sustainable materials: cotton rope, linen, solid wood (beech, oak), unglazed ceramic, organic soy wax, and cotton. Every product page includes a detailed Materials tab.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-item__question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('faq-item--open')">Where do you ship from?</div>
        <div class="faq-item__answer"><p>All orders ship from our warehouse in Germany. We ship to all EU countries with DHL.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-item__question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('faq-item--open')">How long does delivery take?</div>
        <div class="faq-item__answer"><p>Germany: 2-4 business days. EU: 4-7 business days. Orders placed before 14:00 CET ship the same day.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-item__question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('faq-item--open')">Can I return an item?</div>
        <div class="faq-item__answer"><p>Yes! You have 30 days from delivery to return any unused item in its original packaging. See our <a href="/pages/shipping" style="color:#C17F59;text-decoration:underline;">Shipping & Returns</a> page for details.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-item__question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('faq-item--open')">Are your products handmade?</div>
        <div class="faq-item__answer"><p>Yes. The majority of our products are handcrafted by skilled artisans. This means each piece has natural variations in texture, color, and finish — that's the beauty of wabi-sabi.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-item__question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('faq-item--open')">Do you offer wholesale?</div>
        <div class="faq-item__answer"><p>We're currently building our wholesale program. Reach out at hello@aeladaily.com and we'll be happy to discuss.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

